sets.name: Diamond Kings
notes: #DK-1 through #DK-14 and #DK-29 inserted in Series 1 packs
#DK-15 through #DK-28 and #DK-30 inserted in Series 2 packs

sets.name: Special Edition
notes: Cards #1-50 have the same photos and design as base #1-50, while cards #51-100 have the same photos and design as base #331-380.
Cards have holofoil stamping on the front and a "Special Edition" holofoil stamp (with card number) on the upper back.
